n Americans, and young voters; where the G.O.P. is headed beyond Trump=E2=
=80=99s second term; and what the future holds for J.D. Vance as a potentia=
l MAGA successor. (Disclosure: Ruffini=E2=80=99s firm, Echelon Insights, do=
es some polling for Puck.) Our conversation has been lightly edited. You ca=
